### Erstellen
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/geotags
content-type: application/json

{
    "latitude": 19.569603,
    "longitude": -165.654487,
    "name": "Pacific",
    "hashtag": "#coolPlace"
}


### Auslesen [1/2]
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/geotags

### Auslesen [2/2]
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/geotags/11


### Ändern
PUT http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/geotags/11
content-type: application/json

{
    "latitude": 19.569603,
    "longitude": -165.654487,
    "name": "Pacific",
    "hashtag": "#edu"
}


### Suchen [1/3]
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/geotags?searchterm=%23edu

### Suchen [2/3]
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/geotags?latitude=19.57&longitude=-165.6545

### Suchen [3/3]
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/geotags?latitude=19.57&longitude=-165.6545?searchterm=cif

### Löschen
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/geotags/11